Privacy Policy for AAC Serve (https://serve.aaconline.co.uk)

Contact Details:
For the latest contact information, please see this document: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Auto-Accident-Claims/notices/main/legal-notice

Types of Data Collected:

Usage Data is collected automatically when using the Service so that we may improve our service to you.

Usage Data may include information such as Your Device's Internet Protocol address (e.g. IP address), browser type, browser version, the pages of our Service that You visit, the time and date of Your visit, the time spent on those pages, unique device identifiers and other diagnostic data.

Usage data may be held for upto 30 days before being discarded.

We only use session cookies which are are essential to authenticate users. We only use these cookies to provide access to the service.

We do not use any third party analytics services (e.g. Google Analytics)

We do not pass your data on to any third party.

If you are provided an account by us, we will collect from you and store your name and email address for the purposes of providing service to the website.
If you have an account and do not wish to use the service anymore, please contact us and we will remove your details from our records.

Our service may contain links to other websites not operated by us. If You click on a third party link, You will be directed to that third party's site. We strongly advise you to review the Privacy Policy of every site you visit.

You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, You can contact us:

    By post: Sureland House, Journeymans Way, Southend-on-Sea, Essex SS2 5TF

